      <h3 class="font-heading text-[24px] font-medium leading-[1.2] text-[#1D2F40] mb-4">Quality Product</h3>
      <p class="font-body text-[16px] leading-[1.5] text-[#7A7A7A]">Our meticulous attention to detail and stringent quality control processes ensure that every product leaving our factory meets the highest standards of excellence.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 3 -->
    <div class="p-8 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
      <div class="h-[75px] w-[75px] mb-6">
        <img src="/images/services/Icon-3-1.png" alt="Trusted by Clients" class="w-full h-full object-contain" />
      </div>
      <h3 class="font-heading text-[24px] font-medium leading-[1.2] text-[#1D2F40] mb-4">Trusted by Clients</h3>
      <p class="font-body text-[16px] leading-[1.5] text-[#7A7A7A]">20 years track record of delivering exceptional sportswear solutions has earned us the trust and loyalty of numerous satisfied clients worldwide</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
